CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776110751
OL,3,CHillsborough Law Now director
OL,4,C'unsurprised' by Southport inquiry
OL,6,FThe director of the Hillsborough Law
OL,7,FNow campaign says the findings of the
OL,8,FSouthport inquiry are 'unsurprising'
OL,9,Fand believes 'there is a real risk of
OL,10,Fit happening again'.
OL,12,FElkan Arbrahamson was reacting to the
OL,13,Ffindings of the inquiry which found
OL,14,Fthose involved in the care and
OL,15,Fmonitoring of the Southport killer
OL,16,F'fundamentally failed' to appreciate
OL,17,Fthe "evident high level of danger" he
OL,18,Fposed - leading to an "act of chilling
OL,19,Fbrutality".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
