OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776110751
OL,3,CHillsborough Law Now director
OL,4,C'unsurprised' by Southport inquiry
OL,6,FAR - as he has been known throughout
OL,7,Fthe inquiry - murdered Bebe King, six,
OL,8,FElsie Dot Stancombe, seven, and Alice
OL,9,Fda Silva Aguiar, nine, at a Taylor
OL,10,FSwift-themed dance class on 29 July
OL,11,F2024.
OL,13,FThe Southport Inquiry, held over nine
OL,14,Fweeks at Liverpool Town Hall in 2025,
OL,15,Flooked at what happened before and
OL,16,Fduring the attack, identifying missed
OL,17,Fopportunities and systemic failures.
OL,19,FHowever, Mr Arbrahamson questioned the
OL,20,Fultimate outcome of holding inquiries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776110751
OL,3,CHillsborough Law Now director
OL,4,C'unsurprised' by Southport inquiry
OL,6,F"It is frightening, but it's across
OL,7,Fall sectors", he said.
OL,9,F"I mean, look at the Covid inquiry.
OL,10,FWe've had a report from two stages so
OL,11,Ffar. I don't think we are, as a
OL,12,Fcountry, any better prepared for a
OL,13,Fpandemic than we were ten years ago."
OL,15,FIn a damning report, Chair of the
OL,16,FSouthport Iniquiry, Sir Adrian
OL,17,FFulford, concluded he was almost
OL,18,Fcertain "this terrible event could
OL,19,Fhave been - and should have been -
OL,20,Fprevented."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776110751
OL,3,CHillsborough Law Now director
OL,4,C'unsurprised' by Southport inquiry
OL,6,F"To some extent you could have written
OL,7,Fthe report before the inquiry started
OL,8,Fand in fact, before the tragedy
OL,9,Foccurred.
OL,11,F"It's always about agencies not taking
OL,12,Fresponsibility, agencies not speaking
OL,13,Fto each other, lack of coordination,
OL,14,Fnot spotting warning signs that are
OL,15,Fquite clear in retrospect and should
OL,16,Fhave been quite clear before.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776110751
OL,3,CHillsborough Law Now director
OL,4,C'unsurprised' by Southport inquiry
OL,6,F"I think there's less of a risk of
OL,7,Fthat happening here, because there was
OL,8,Fa phase two, and the phase two will
OL,9,Fprovide the chair of the inquiry with
OL,10,Fthe opportunity to monitor the
OL,11,Frecommendations that come out of phase
OL,12,Fone.
OL,14,FWhen asked if the 66 recommendations
OL,15,Fwill be 'taken seriously', he said:
OL,16,F"Unless the recommendations are
OL,17,Fimplemented in full, certainly with
OL,18,Fregards to interagency cooperation and
OL,19,Fresponsibility and so on, there's a
OL,20,Freal risk of it happening again.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776110751
OL,3,CHillsborough Law Now director
OL,4,C'unsurprised' by Southport inquiry
OL,6,F"I think you need an independent
OL,7,Fmonitoring body to monitor the
OL,8,Frecommendations of inquiries.
OL,10,F"I think if we looked at the form and
OL,11,Fstructure that inquiries take, we
OL,12,Fcould probably conduct effective
OL,13,Finquiries a lot more cheaply.
OL,15,F"Looking at looking at them as a
OL,16,Fwhole, there may be some way you need
OL,17,Fthe full role of voice of a statutory
OL,18,Finquiry, but there may be others when
OL,19,Fyou don't.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776110751
OL,3,CHillsborough Law Now director
OL,4,C'unsurprised' by Southport inquiry
OL,6,F"We're recommending a duty of candour
OL,7,Fand trying to get Hillsborough law
OL,8,Fpassed, and if a duty of candour were
OL,9,Fimplemented, then the need for a
OL,10,Fstatutory inquiry diminishes, because
OL,11,Fthe Inquiries Act requires people to
OL,12,Ftell the truth and impose penalties if
OL,13,Fyou don't."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
